53.8	Sylar	Sylar	Gabriel Gray, more commonly known by his pseudonym; Sylar (the brand name of a watch he encountered as a watchmaker), is one of the primary antagonists in the NBC drama Heroes. Portrayed by Zachary Quinto, he is a superpowered serial killer who targets other superhumans in order to steal their powers. He served as the primary villain of the first season and then as a recurring antagonist. After being rescued from a mental prison by Peter Petrelli in "The Wall", Sylar has now identified himself as a hero in "Brave New World".	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/b/b3/Gabriel_Gray.jpg/200px-Gabriel_Gray.jpg
